---
// Testimonials with graffiti wall aesthetic
---

<section id="testimonials" class="relative py-32 bg-ink text-paper overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Graffiti texture background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute top-10 left-20 font-graffiti text-[200px] text-punk transform -rotate-12">REAL</div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-10 font-graffiti text-[150px] text-electric transform rotate-6">TALK</div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/3 font-graffiti text-[180px] text-acid transform -rotate-3">RAW</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="font-graffiti text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl mb-4">
        <span class="text-neon-pink">ARTISTS SPEAK</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="font-mono text-xl uppercase tracking-widest">
        No paid actors. Just real artists who can afford groceries now.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Testimonials grid - asymmetric layout -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="md:col-span-7 relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-punk blur-xl opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-ink border-4 border-punk p-8 transform rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform">
          <p class="font-mono text-xl mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            "Jenna turned my shoebox of receipts and existential dread into 
            actual financial statements. Found $4,200 in deductions I didn't 
            know existed. Now I can afford therapy AND new canvases."
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-punk rounded-full"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold">Sarah M.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-punk">Mixed Media Artist, New Haven</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 md:mt-12 relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-electric blur-xl opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-ink border-4 border-electric p-8 transform -rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform">
          <p class="font-mono text-lg mb-6">
            "First bookkeeper who didn't judge my 'filing system' 
            (aka the floor). She just... fixed it."
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-electric rounded-full"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold">Marcus T.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-electric">Sculptor, Hartford</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-acid blur-xl opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-ink border-4 border-acid p-8 transform rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform">
          <p class="font-mono text-lg mb-6">
            "Applied for a grant. They wanted 3 years of financials. 
            Had them in 24 hours. Got the grant. ðŸ¤¯"
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-acid rounded-full"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold">Kim L.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-acid">Photographer, Stamford</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Testimonial 4 -->
      <div class="md:col-span-7 md:-mt-8 relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-violet blur-xl opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-ink border-4 border-violet p-8 transform -rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform">
          <p class="font-mono text-xl mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            "I was trading paintings for rent and had no idea how to 
            report it. Jenna made it make sense. Even set up a system 
            so I can track everything on my phone between studio sessions."
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-violet rounded-full"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold">Alex R.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-violet">Painter, Middletown</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Stats bar -->
    <div class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="font-graffiti text-5xl text-punk">50+</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase">Artists Saved</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="font-graffiti text-5xl text-electric">$200K+</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase">Deductions Found</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="font-graffiti text-5xl text-acid">0</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase">IRS Letters</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="font-graffiti text-5xl text-violet">100%</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase">Vibes</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>